Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入學式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:12.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照假名的順序決定座位，相川是「あ」開頭坐最前，櫟井是「い」開頭排第二。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是相川  所以每次總是坐在最前面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊坐的是「い」…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫟井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有點兒不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的話那本很厚的入學指南裡有詳細地寫著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能在暑假裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一直很在意的櫟井同學她們的關係能夠變得更好一些的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野野原同學的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發給我這個  我要怎麼回覆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:03:00.07,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,120)\fad(500,500)}班長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  今天野野原同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她跑哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  剛才那個是誰來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認識嗎  體育課的時候還一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太擅長記住別人的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的  話說這是有臉大聲講出來的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柚子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這算是故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你帶了個眼鏡來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  為了以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你在學校幾乎不戴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想被人看出我很聰明的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來確實挺聰明的  只不過想法上有點蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  聽我說聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從今天早上開始狀態就特別的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多好呢  有多好的狀態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該是「不錯喲」「真好啊」這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  看出你姿勢不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說狀態好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說是幹勁？  感覺幹勁十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼好不容易有這機會  就要好好為他人服務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這一手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這一手嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼停頓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子  拿出點幹勁來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？拿出點？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹勁光線？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這種意思嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是從指頭裡出來的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  下次一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有也去下那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:28.51,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺提心吊膽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才盡情地沐浴了幹勁光線啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子  光線是什麼系的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間差系？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹勁…全部都放出來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易有的幹勁  在上課前就用光了要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說些讓我有幹勁的台詞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤…烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好沉重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親子丼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河豚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芒果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松茸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚子醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.81,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼全都是食物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥鵝肝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北極貝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松本老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  請問怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫您拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「媽媽」一詞已經深入人心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去社團活動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  昨晚我玩拼圖時想到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾會看到一塊這種形狀的  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課上你居然畫這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好喜歡那種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是反過來又感覺很討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前拼過一個大海的拼圖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那拼圖是什麼圖案的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偉人系列
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛因斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼選了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成的瞬間感覺IQ會提升20厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的錯覺  話說厘米是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小相相  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？這感覺是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在書店搞好關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要去社團活動？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小相相回見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近被其他同學也稱呼為媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為媽媽完全表現出了媽媽的樣子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完…完全表現嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒辦法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法的話那確實也只能沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是沒辦法的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  完全沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那媽媽來當我們的媽媽就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子沒有媽媽的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  媽媽…一次  一次就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以好好喊你一聲媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個…老師我可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這演的是哪一出？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  就一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿媽媽嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師已經不知道什麼是正確答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒有什麼正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  我只是想忽悠你一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這品性真是太壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是青春期孩子們特有的對大人的那什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  真是複雜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生隨著年齡的成長總會來的那什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況不能用這種說法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春期哦  很麻煩的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被一個不經意的意外傷害到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如玻璃一般哦  很容易碎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纖細柔弱到爆的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春期還真是讓人勞神啊  真是討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  她們都是胡說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母都還健在  完全不是什麼玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是鐵板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用青春期來做擋箭牌  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事的  老師就是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這般劣性的我以後也還可以稱呼您為媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿媽媽  Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽嗎  我還很年輕的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是松本老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽嗎  感覺這樣看大家都變得很可愛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要老找老師麻煩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天的主題就定為鯨魚好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是鯨魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  我對媽媽的愛就如同鯨魚一般大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對小唯的愛也像鯨魚一樣大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然到現在才說　我們老這樣隨意地決定主題真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？網上說座頭鯨的歌聲恐怕是動物界中最複雜的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄性會在交配期歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那鯨魚是為了攻陷女朋友而唱那麼難度拔群的歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺形象改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌嗎  好羞人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇  長鬚鯨的心臟居然有600公斤重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最粗的血管直徑有20cm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好粗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能唱歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  那個很羞人的鯨魚是座頭鯨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？長須先生不唱歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:47.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長須鯨（ながすくじら）和長瀬（ながせ）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不叫得像長瀨先生似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面說睡覺的時候也在游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左腦和右腦交替休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:13:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼迷迷糊糊的長鬚鯨  時而像理科生時而充滿藝術細胞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在有點困了  屬於哪種呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  52x31x86=？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微費點時間可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這僅僅是犯迷糊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:30.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1160,140)}佐藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說利用超聲波來交流資訊的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:30.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,200)}史密斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果血緣相差太遠的話交流起來是很困難的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這樣說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的親戚說我好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的親戚說我沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說下DNA和河馬是近親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？河馬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那鯨魚是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再順便說下它們有四個胃 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯨魚是什麼星人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地球的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:08.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs30}鯨魚總結
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:08.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs30}不管好壞總之很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:08.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs30}本體是啥不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:08.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs30}總覺得沒法討厭它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  鯨魚  到頭來也沒怎麼弄明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯨魚的種種都好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不像是總結的總結
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}鯨魚總結
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}有點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…感覺好困
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電池用完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠悠式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙  早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  沒勁的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小說太好看了  一口氣看完直接早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷史小說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼程度？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋小唯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一節是英語來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}什麼程度「どのくらい」和「Don't cry」發音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  不是Don't cry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯因為太困變成笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦  不管發生了什麼我們都一直在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我是媽媽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是媽媽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好複雜的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要這樣哦  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  快醒醒  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點  快起來  快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.35,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽我都準備好了膝枕  快點來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵  給吾退下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是武士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有兩個媽媽了  再加上笨蛋唯武士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐槽點太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你倆趕緊滾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,660)\fs32}Don't cry
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離午休還有多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  英語？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩節課哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才要說「我沒哭」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟蹋了睡意中的小唯使出渾身解數想出來的段子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒那個打算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  對不起  我沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的你們倆別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再輕鬆歡樂一些  什麼都不想地聊聊天就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士超人戰士的外號一定是武士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子同學總是好突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候會想吃羊棲菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pheromone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)\fs30}動物激素
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單詞？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是什麼都沒在想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:37.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}法國的啟蒙思想家。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孟…孟…孟德斯鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Pheromone「フェロモン」應該用「n」來接，但在詞語接龍裡是犯規的。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我用「孟」來接了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人有時會完全鑽牛角尖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡  雖然說看不到摸不著  事實上是有空氣存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你還是用腦子想想再說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  再有一節課就午休了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像克服了睡眠的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  讓我襲胸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在這裡  進屋再說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫟井同學  沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是相川同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…接著就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫟井同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從早上開始好像就不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來她真熬不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一節課的老師是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神崎老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去和她說聲  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把睡相拍下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！我也要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔弱的小唯好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也來一張  我拍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍…拍下來可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來拍吧來拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是別人發而是自己拍下來的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有朋友的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是偷拍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去廁所的時間好長  便秘嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才去把櫟井同學扶到保健室去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副高興的樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得絕症了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緣？  柚子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在學校  不要啊  好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課已經都上完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你  我幫你把包拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能起得來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  還困嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要再睡一會兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  小唯  把你內褲脫了對不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還穿著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
