Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被叫做「鼻煙」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.13,0:23:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.59,0:23:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子的手好漂亮啊
